      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer" id="contact">
    <div class="footer-content">
      <div class="footer-about">
        <strong>About us:</strong> Helping JEE aspirants make informed college choices with data and technology.
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
